Pod-Coverage-Careful

This module is a more careful version of Pod::Coverage.  See 
its pod for details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
man command.

    man Pod::Coverage::Careful

If you are not on a Unix-like system or emulation thereof, you may be
force to use this instead:

    perldoc Pod::Coverage::Careful

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Pod-Coverage-Careful

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Pod-Coverage-Careful

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Pod-Coverage-Careful

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Pod-Coverage-Careful/


